Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来和第二位的分差就是29000点…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  薄墨如果自摸役满的话就可以缩小到21000点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.61,0:00:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果直击清澄的话  和第二位的分差就是15800点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…要放弃塞她吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然我也有可能放铳薄墨的役满…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过对役满毫无戒备的庄家应该离死更近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被打倒吧  全国中学联赛冠军！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.86,0:03:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没听…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听牌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.34,0:03:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长说过的小四喜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常的偶然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到两副露就自然地弃和了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…这样也很正常呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样  薄墨的北家还有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后怎样先不说  总之我得努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,断幺宝牌2  三本场6100点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6100点的直击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放铳的薄墨选手  后半战到现在也没有和过牌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立直
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立直
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.73,0:04:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3900
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.74,0:04:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  这样优势又增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看着吧  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易能跟着你在同一个大会里出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里开始…我一步也不想退后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闲家2000  庄家4000
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬松的爱宕娟惠选手  满贯自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东三局和四局连续和牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  继续加油啊  小娟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从姐姐接过来的点数
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量要守住  有可能的话还想增加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么以姬松居首的战况  后半战也终于进入了南场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外的是永水的薄墨选手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到目前已经有25000以上的负分了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三所学校的对薄墨对策
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:06:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否可以看作是很好地发挥了效果了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  刚才那一把薄墨选手也役满听牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到这个程度与其说是对策  更不如说是气力上的比拼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然被宫守的团子头给…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来确实如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这一局又轮到小初坐北家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薄墨最后的北家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要这里能安全度过的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立直
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北拿到了也不能打
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗杠也行？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里如果清澄放铳  我们就能升到二位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有理由塞住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杠宝牌增加了  第二位的庄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清澄又已经立直
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…薄墨已经集齐了东和北
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  放铳吧清澄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撑住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闲家8000  庄家16000哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,役满  小四喜炸裂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薄墨选手  在南场后半终于爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二位的清澄被炸庄  痛失了大量点数
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无动摇？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小四喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点和  3900
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副将战  结束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:09:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么副将战的结果出炉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四校的点数大体上没有变化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一位的依然是姬松高校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副将的爱宕娟惠选手  继姐姐之后出色地守住了一位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后是去年的全国中学联赛冠军原村和选手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以少量正分保持住了二位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永水的薄墨选手漂亮地凭借役满从末位升至三位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宫守的臼泽选手虽然打法稳健但得分并未增加  最终位列第四
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打完一看结果是最后一名…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.94,0:10:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然一定程度上预料到了  但还是很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丰音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:10:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  落到最后一名了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有哦  塞已经很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才能以这个分差就了结了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就靠你了  丰音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我会努力的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  差不多也该上场了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久违的出场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  大将战在三位开始  这还是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次如果我变成那样的话也还请多多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.59,0:11:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了哦  小莳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次在全国大赛大展身手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手一搏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:11:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了  小和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  咲也要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大会第六日第三场比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大将战马上就要拉开序幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能多赚点分数  真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绢你在说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你守住了头名位置  更加昂首挺胸点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然之后  我的立场很艰难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:12:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油  恭子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.30,0:13:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,末原学姐为什么说立场艰难…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭子确实不是很有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手看上去也很强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是从来没有抱着会输的想法坐在麻将桌旁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是恭子无论对手多么弱都会考虑输掉的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为如此她才强大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是恭子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想有朝一日能够被姐姐所期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赌上八强名额的战斗终于将要拉下帷幕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.03,0:14:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大将战马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.43,0:14:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前半战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杠材  下一张自摸手牌是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀  那这个就只能抱着不放了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3900
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自摸  1000  2000
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点和  2600
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连和三次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬松的大将末原选手  开局以来连续三次和牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没给其它学校任何接近的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很着急呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了逃跑把档加到最快了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庄家吗  没有平时那么开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听牌  本来考虑到流局的情况  而没有选择超快速和牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但就算是庄家也得进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立直
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清澄！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岭上开花  8000
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是岭上开花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大明杠后岭上开花的包牌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然已经预想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个清澄的大将  是在某种条件能够发挥支配力的类型么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岭上开花的出现几率虽然很小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是宫永选手的和牌中很多是岭上开花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实  她的成绩和数据让人有点难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然连续三次和牌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但之前的包牌和立直棒  送出去9000点  基本上扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立直
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想追立呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能过的话  就立直
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.89,0:18:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立直  一发  宝牌1  5200
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四面张输给了边张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然想这么说  但这其实也挺常见的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种手牌也追立啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立直
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手气依旧很好  继续进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能过的话～我就追立立直哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被庄家追立真不舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点和
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立直  一发  3900
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被追立  然后又一发放铳了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然想认为只是偶然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1300  2600  再加一本场100  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岭上开花  每人500
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有岭上开花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是有必定能和牌的自信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立直
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.21,0:20:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能过的话  就立直
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是紧跟不舍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宫守的姊带选手  这已经是第三次追立了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一次都是追的姬松的末原选手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2900
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来？这已经是第三次了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地区预选和一回战她应该都没有追立过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.11,0:20:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丰音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  非常成功呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在为止靠着大家的活跃才隐藏至今呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连续三次追立？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且都是一发
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追立后就能够直击先立直的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种不可思议的事情到底会不会有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止的比赛她都不是很显眼  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.89,0:21:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此  想要再试一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.09,0:21:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立直
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次如果还不行  那之后就暗听
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.42,0:21:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.33,0:21:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能过的话  就立直
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子在故乡的绰号是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.56,0:21:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「背后的丰音」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.19,0:22:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于先制者  会从背后绞杀之
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.84,0:22:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,------
